     3	#: 21212 S13/Virtual Reality
     4	    08-Nov-91  15:30:58
     5	Sb: Virtual reality
     6	Fm: Matt Drury 75300,1610
     7	To: All
     8	
     9	The Virtual Reality section here in the Computer Art Forum has now been opened
    10	for public use. John Eagan [76130,2225] is the section leader.
    11	
    12	The goal of this section is to create, much as the fractals group in area 15
    13	have, a virtual reality system that can be used on personal computers that are
    14	readily available. Based on the response I have seen to my public request for
    15	interested people, and the experience that the people who have contacted me
    16	have should make this easily possible.
    17	
    18	  Matt Drury
    19	  Graphics Forums Staff
    20	
    21	
    22	
    23	
