    29	
    30	The timing for opening this section is just great... my PowerGlove and Sega
    31	3D glasses projects are just now starting give results.  This will be great
    32	place to swap notes with others playing (er, working) with the same things.
    33	 
    34	It's going to be tough to figure out exactly where to post messages, though,
    35	when a project involves an Amateur doing a Raytraced 3-D Animation.  (Such
    36	troubles I can live with!)
