    46	
    47	Mike- Post them here! Welcome to the section, your message is the first
    48	"non-official" one in the section! How does it feel to be a pioneer?<g> 
    49	Anything of interest you have, let's see it. The funny thing is, the nature of
    50	the subject here inherently means that a lot of boundaries will be crossed, so
    51	don't pick too many nits about "does it really belong here", especially until
    52	things start taking direction. We can sort that stuff out after some things
    53	are on the table, as it were.
